    <thetext>Description of problem:
When launching the media writer, the GUI presents French rather than the primary system language (English).

Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable):
FedoraMediaWriter-osx-4.0.4.dmg

How reproducible:
Always

Steps to Reproduce:
1. Download FedoraMediaWriter-osx-4.0.4.dmg
2. open the disk image
3. launch the application

Actual results:
FMW uses French GUI

Expected results:
FMW uses English GUI

Additional info:
1) French and Spanish are set as the secondary and tertiary languages on this computer
2) OS: macOS Sierra 10.12.1</thetext>
